original_title: Sixty Nine: A Celebration Of Gay Sex
overview: On the heels of their best selling photo book, Sixty Nine: Joyful Gay Sex, Jake & RJ have created a collection of some of their favorite scenes that have continued to inspire their work, love and relationship. Featuring Colby Keller, Levi Karter, Dale Cooper, Gabriel Clark & Tayte Hanson, this volume contains the best and hottest of the gay sexual experience.
title: Sixty Nine: A Celebration Of Gay Sex
